sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant drand as drand Beacon
    participant Lit as Lit Protocol
    participant FWSS as Filecoin Warm Storage
    participant Contract as WayneLockGuardianRecovery
    participant FPay as Filecoin Pay

    Note over User,FPay: Step 0 - Fund Storage Rail
    User->>FPay: depositAndApprove(amount)
    FPay->>FPay: ERC-20 approve + deposit USDFC

    Note over User,FPay: Step 1 - Generate Password
    Browser->>Browser: crypto.getRandomValues 32 bytes
    Browser->>drand: Fetch latest round R1
    drand-->>Browser: R1 verified 32 bytes
    Browser->>drand: Fetch previous round R2
    drand-->>Browser: R2 verified 32 bytes
    Browser->>Browser: HKDF then scrypt then LocalKey
    Browser->>Browser: HKDF then scrypt then password_bytes
    Browser->>Browser: Map to charset

    Note over User,FPay: Step 2 - Encrypt Password
    Browser->>Browser: Generate DEK 32 random bytes
    Browser->>Browser: AES-GCM encrypt password with DEK
    Browser->>Lit: litEncryptDek with accessConditions
    Note right of Lit: ACC checks isRecoveryApprovedForOwner
    Lit-->>Browser: litCiphertext + dataToEncryptHash

    Note over User,FPay: Step 3 - Upload to Filecoin Wallet Popup 1
    Browser->>FWSS: uploadVaultBlob encryptedBlob
    FWSS->>FWSS: Pad to 127 bytes and calculate pieceCid
    FWSS->>FWSS: uploadPiece then findPiece poll
    User->>FWSS: createDataSetAndAddPieces MetaMask Sign
    FWSS-->>Browser: pieceCid + serviceURL

    Note over User,FPay: Step 4 - On-chain Registration Wallet Popup 2
    Browser->>Browser: Build metadataJson
    alt First time vault not initialized
        User->>Contract: registerVaultAndAddEntry MetaMask Sign
        Contract->>Contract: Set guardians + threshold + add entry
    else Subsequent entries
        User->>Contract: addEntry MetaMask Sign
    end
    Contract-->>Browser: tx hash confirmed
